Kristen Cloke https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kristen_Cloke 0 Kristen Ann Cloke (born September 2, 1968) is an American actress. She appeared in Space: Above and Beyond, and has acted in several small parts of other TV series as well as a role in Final Destination.
